tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE dna_sequences (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  sequence TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Sequences (id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
sequence TEXT);

CREATE TABLE Genes (id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
sequence_id UUID,
gene_name TEXT,
FOREIGN KEY (sequence_id) REFERENCES Sequences(id));

CREATE TABLE Mutations (id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
gene_id UUID,
mutation_description TEXT,
FOREIGN KEY (gene_id) REFERENCES Genes(id));

CREATE TABLE Annotations (id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
mutation_id UUID,
annotation TEXT,
FOREIGN KEY (mutation_id) REFERENCES Mutations(id));
